1:20:40.076 --> 1:20:42.274
What the hell
does that even mean?

1:20:42.309 --> 1:20:45.508
Buncha knotheads pointin'
a camera at themselves.

1:20:45.543 --> 1:20:47.345
I thought you handled it
really well.

1:20:47.380 --> 1:20:49.380
