<i>Aw, c'mon.</i>

1:25:00.028 --> 1:25:02.171
Honey, you look really cute.

1:27:47.734 --> 1:27:49.195
Give me your hand.

1:27:49.230 --> 1:27:50.900
The baby's really kicking.

1:28:03.882 --> 1:28:05.585
I'll be right back.

