1:30:00.130 --> 1:30:04.132
<i>♪ I know you have</i>
<i>A lot of strength left ♪</i>

1:30:04.167 --> 1:30:07.905
<i>♪ I know you have</i>
<i>A little life in you yet ♪</i>

